    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The makers of Progress Bar Simulator (the most realistic simulation of progress bars ever created) bringing you a new epic experience.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147600/extras/9dc1b6beb2da1483199b646ffbf3a285.avif?t=1744375563\" width=616 height=185 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone, with friends in private rooms or join a faction and play online with the whole world in this epic MMORPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >On Deck</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case you are &quot;on the go&quot; and desperately need to flip a switch, we will be there for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light Switch Simulator has (at least we aim for) 100% Steam Deck compatibility.<br>We are also way cheaper than other &quot;switches&quot; on the go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* 3 factions with an EPIC back story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Unlock epic light switches</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Turn the lights on</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Turn The lights off</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147600/extras/150aec47eb3f845e3a2f969800afc475.avif?t=1744375563\" width=616 height=252 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Turn the lights on</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Turn The lights off</p>",
